body:
It seems that everyone is getting annoyed at the lower priority queues, and yes i&#039;m annoyed with them too. I mean ive got at least 3 20min queues and its not really my fault the internet keeps disconnecting. 
Anyway I decided to do something else while waiting, normally i come back from school then play and have my food. Now I just turn on lol and eat my food while waiting for the queues to finish. Anyway I know that nobody will really care about this but we should do something else while waiting for the queues.
PS. Just cause I want a reply - what is the highest queue time we can get. Thx {{champion:154}}
